Package: perturbplanApp
Title: Constraint-Driven Experimental Design for CRISPR Perturb-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Ziang", "Niu", , "ziangniu@wharton.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Yihui", "He", , "yihuihe@wharton.upenn.edu", role = c("aut")),
      person("Eugene", "Katsevich", , "ekatsevi@wharton.upenn.edu", role = c("aut"))
    )
Description: Golem-based Shiny application for constraint-driven
    experimental design and power analysis in CRISPR perturb-seq
    experiments. Provides intuitive interface for optimization objectives,
    parameter constraints, and workflow-specific analysis.
